NK041(di)019:1: // rten gsum rab tu gnas pa'i cho ga snying por
NK041(di)019:2: dril ba dge legs char 'bebs zhes bya ba bzhugs
NK041(di)019:3: so // na mahsh+ri gu ra be /
NK041(di)019:4: shin tu rnam par dag pa'i ye shes ni //
NK041(di)019:5: gang 'dul sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i rol mo can //
NK041(di)019:6: brtan g.yo kun la khyab pa'i he ru ka /
NK041(di)019:7: dpal ldan rdo rje sems dpas dge legs mdzod //
NK041(di)019:8: de la 'dir su pra tish+tha'i sgra las drangs na
NK041(di)019:9: de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyi tshad ma med phrin
NK041(di)019:10: las kyis sprul pa'i gzugs brnyan sku gsung thugs kyi
NK041(di)019:11: rten dam tshig pa'i rnam char shar ba la /
NK041(di)019:12: ye shes pa legs par rab tu gnas pa'i cho
NK041(di)019:13: ga ni rdo rje 'chang chen pos rgyud sde rgya
NK041(di)019:14: mtsho nas lan cig ma yin par basngagasa pa'i tshul
NK041(di)019:17: sa la sogs las phyag rgya byas //
NK041(di)019:19: dag pa'i ye shes kyis sbyangs par //
NK041(di)019:20: smos ci dgos te de nyid yin //
NK041(di)019:21: zhes pa la sogs pas mtshon te rgya cher gsungs
NK041(di)019:22: pa'i dgongs don dang 'brel bar grub pa'i slob dpon
NK041(di)019:23: rnams kyis legs par bkral ba'i tshul las mdor bsdus
NK041(di)019:24: pa tsam ji ltar bya ba la'ang gsum ste /
NK041(di)019:28: mtshan nyid dang ldan pa'i rten gyi mdun sogs skabs phyed pa /
NK041(di)019:29: gang la brten pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi yo byad dang /
NK041(di)019:31: bye brag tu rab gnas la dgos pa'i mnga' 'bul gyi man+dala /
NK041(di)019:33: mchod pa'i bye brag sogs 'og tu nye bar mkho
NK041(di)019:34: ba rnams ma tshang ba med par 'du bya zhing
NK041(di)019:35: / bkod pas mdzes par bshams nas /
NK041(di)019:36: dkyil 'khor gang la brten pa'i las gzung srangs rjes bzlas pa'i mthar /
NK041(di)019:37: rnam bum du lha tshogs rnams lhag par gsal bas gzungs thag la 'jus te /
NK041(di)019:38: rang gi thugs ka nas sngags kyi phreng ba byung /
NK041(di)019:39: gzungs thag la 'khril te bum pa'i nang du song bas lha tshogs rnams kyi thugs rgyud bskul /
NK041(di)019:40: 'od zer spro bsdus don gnyis mdzad /
NK041(di)019:41: sku'i cha thams cad nas byang sems bdud rtsi'i rgyun babs pas bum pa gang bar gyur bsams la /
NK041(di)019:42: rtsa sngags kyi sham bur dbyangs gsal rten snying su pra tish+tha rnams sbrel ba ci nus bzla /
NK041(di)019:44: las thams cad kyi bum par pad nyi'i gdan la
NK041(di)019:45: h'u las khro bo bdud rtsi 'khyil pa skad cig
NK041(di)019:46: gis gsal ba'i sku las rdo rje bdud rtsi'i rdul
NK041(di)019:47: phra rab babs pas bum pa gang bar bsam la
NK041(di)019:48: / badz+ra a mri ta kun+da l+ai ha na ha
NK041(di)019:49: na h'u phata dang khrus sngags a b+hi she ka'ang
NK041(di)019:50: / bzla / mthar mchod cing bstod la /
NK041(di)019:51: yi ge brgya pas nongs pa bshags /
NK041(di)019:52: +aahmh'u gis dung chos kyi chu mchod yon du phul
NK041(di)019:53: bas bum pa'i lha 'od du zhu ba bum chu
NK041(di)019:54: dang dbyer med ro gcig tu gyur par bsam /
NK041(di)019:55: rig pa'i me tog dor ba tsam gyis bdag nyid 'jug pa'ang bya'o //
NK041(di)019:56: gnyis pa rab gnas dngos kyi cho ga la rnam grangs bcu gcig las /
NK041(di)019:58: gtor ma gsum re re nas rten la bskor zhing /
NK041(di)019:59: sarba big+han+na na ma s+sarba ta th+aa ga ta b+h+yo bi shwa sogs lan gsum gyis zhi ba /
NK041(di)019:60: ting lo dang chang bus bskor zhing /
NK041(di)019:61: sum+b+ha ni gsum gyi phyed ma /
NK041(di)019:62: badz+ra ma h+aa sh+ri he ru ko&a ham /
NK041(di)019:63: rang nyid skad cig gis rdo rje h'u mdzad khro
NK041(di)019:64: bo'i rgyal po 'jigs su rung ba'i skur gyur pa'i
NK041(di)019:65: dpral bar mgrin par +aah thugs kar h'u /
NK041(di)019:66: h'u las 'od zer 'phros pas khro bo'i sprin rab
NK041(di)019:67: 'byams dpag tu med pa badz+ra sa m+aa dzasa spyan
NK041(di)019:68: drangs / badz+ra kro d+ha r+aa dza sa pa ri w+aa ra ar+g+ham sogs nas /
NK041(di)019:69: shab+da pra tits+tsha s+w+aa h+aa'i bar gyis mchod /
NK041(di)019:71: 'jigs pa'i h'u sgra nges sgrogs shing //
NK041(di)019:72: bgegs rnams ma lus 'joms mdzad pa //
NK041(di)019:73: dngos grub ma lus stsal ba'i lha //
NK041(di)019:74: bgegs kyi dgra la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK041(di)019:76: na mo rje btsun rtsa ba dang brgyud par bcas
NK041(di)019:77: pa'i dpal ldan bla ma dam pa rnams kyi bka'
NK041(di)019:78: bden pa dang / sangs rgyas kyi bka' chos kyi dge 'dun gyi gsang sngags /
NK041(di)019:83: ting nge 'dzin gyi bden chos nyid rnam par dag
NK041(di)019:84: pa'i chos can rgyu 'bras bslu ba med pa'i bden
NK041(di)019:85: bden pa chen po'i byin rlabs kyis sa'i phyogs 'dir
NK041(di)019:86: rdo rje 'dzin pa bdag gis sems rnam pa gnyis
NK041(di)019:87: bskyed de / gnas skabs su 'jig rten gyi khams la phan pa rgya chen po bsgrub pa dang /
NK041(di)019:88: mthar thug sems can thams cad mi gnas pa'i myang
NK041(di)019:89: ngan las 'das pa'i 'bras bu thob par bya ba'i
NK041(di)019:90: ched du bde bar gshegs pa'i sku gsung thugs kyi
NK041(di)019:91: rten rnams la rab tu gnas par bgyi ba la
NK041(di)019:93: glags lta ba'i gang su yang rung ba'i 'byung po
NK041(di)019:94: gdug pa can g.yog dang 'khor du bcas pa rnams
NK041(di)019:95: 'dir ma gnas par gzhan du dengs shig /
NK041(di)019:96: gal te mi 'gro na de bzhin gshegs pa thams
NK041(di)019:97: cad kyi thugs gnyis su med pa'i ye shes las
NK041(di)019:98: byung ba'i khro bo'i ye shes kyi rdo rje rab
NK041(di)019:99: tu 'bar ba 'dis khyed rnams kyi mgo bo tshal
NK041(di)019:101: sum b+ha ni sogs brjod cing /
NK041(di)019:104: rol mo'i tsham rngams dang bcas pas phyi rol du bskrad bzhin drag po'i sbyang ba'o //
NK041(di)019:105: gnyis pa khrus kyi bya ba ni /
NK041(di)019:106: thog mar dkyil khor sogs dang rten ring bsrel can
NK041(di)019:107: gyi gzugs brnyan shar ba'i me long la khrus gsol
NK041(di)019:108: zhing / gang 'dir bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs
NK041(di)019:109: pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs
NK041(di)019:110: rgyas rig pa dang zhabs su ldan pa /
NK041(di)019:113: skyes bu 'dul ba'i kha lo sgyur ba /
NK041(di)019:114: bla na med pa lha dang mi rnams kyi ston
NK041(di)019:115: pa sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das sras dang slob mar
NK041(di)019:116: bcas pa rnams la bdag cag gis yo byad dang
NK041(di)019:117: ldan pa'i sgo nas sku khrus dam pa gsol bar
NK041(di)019:118: bagyi'o // khrus kyi khang pa shin tu dri zhim pa //
NK041(di)019:119: shel gyi sa gzhi gsal zhing 'tsher bar ltar //
NK041(di)019:120: rin chen 'bar ba'i ka ba yid 'ong ldan //
NK041(di)019:121: mu tig 'od chags bla bres pa der //
NK041(di)019:122: de bzhin gshegs pa rnams dang de sras la //
NK041(di)019:123: rin chen bum pa mang po spos kyi chus //
NK041(di)019:124: yid 'ong legs par bkang ba glu dang ni //
NK041(di)019:125: rol mor bcas pa du mas sku khrus gsol //
NK041(di)019:126: ji ltar bltams pa sogs kyi mthar /
NK041(di)019:127: sarba ta th+aa ga ta a b+hi she ga te sa ma la sh+ri ye h'u /
NK041(di)019:130: de dag sku la mtshungs pa med pa'i gos //
NK041(di)019:131: gtsang la dri rab bsgos pas sku phyi'o //
NK041(di)019:132: h'u tram h+r+ai+aahk+aa ya bi sho d+ha ne ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK041(di)019:133: khrus chu de nyid slar yang bum par blugs la /
NK041(di)019:134: rten gsar pa rnams kyi dngos sam gzugs brnyan la khrus gsol zhing /
NK041(di)019:135: 'di ni khrus mchog dpal dang ldan //
NK041(di)019:136: thugs rje'i chu ni bla na med //
NK041(di)019:137: byin brlabs ye shes chu yis ni //
NK041(di)019:138: ci 'dod dngos grub stsol bar mdzod //
NK041(di)019:139: sarba ta tha ga ta sogs /
NK041(di)019:140: 'di ni sbyin pa'i rang bzhin chu //
NK041(di)019:141: ser sna'i dri ma sbyong mdzad cing //
NK041(di)019:142: gtong ba dri yis legs bsgos chu //
NK041(di)019:143: khrus legs mdzad la sku khrus gsol //
NK041(di)019:144: sarba ta th+aa ga ta sogs dang /
NK041(di)019:151: shes rab dang ser sna'i gnas su /
NK041(di)019:157: dang rnams sbyar la so so'i mthar sngags dang bcas pas khrus gsol /
NK041(di)019:158: de dag sku la sogs kyis sku phyi ba rnams bya /
NK041(di)019:159: mthar dri lngas thugs kar byugs la /
NK041(di)019:160: stong gsum kun tu dri ngad ldang gyur pa'i //
NK041(di)019:161: dri mchog rnams kyis thub dbang rnams kyi sku //
NK041(di)019:162: gser sbyangs btso ma byi dor byas pa ltar //
NK041(di)019:163: 'od chags 'bar ba de dag byugs par bgyi //
NK041(di)019:166: de nas de la kha dog legs bsgyur ba'i //
NK041(di)019:167: na bza' shin tu dri zhim dam pa 'bul //
NK041(di)019:168: gos bzang srab la 'jam pa sna tshogs dang //
NK041(di)019:169: rgyan mchog brgya phrag dag kyang dbul bar bgyi //
NK041(di)019:170: badz+ra wastra ye pra tits+tsh+aa s+w+aa h+aa /
NK041(di)019:171: spos mar gyis bdug cing spro na rjes 'brel du shis brjod ji ltar rigs pa'ang bya'o //
NK041(di)019:172: gsum pa rten bskyed pa ni /
NK041(di)019:173: sgrub dkyil gang la brten pa'i mdun bskyed ltar ram /
NK041(di)019:175: a mri ta sa bsang swa b+ha was sbyangs /
NK041(di)019:176: stong pa'i ngang las sku rten dang mchod rten gtsug
NK041(di)019:177: lag khang la sogs pa seng ges btegs pa'i rin
NK041(di)019:178: po che'i khri sna tshogs pad+ma nyi zla brtsegs pa'i
NK041(di)019:179: steng du las 'khor lo dkar po gyis mtshan pa
NK041(di)019:180: las rnam snang dkar po g.yas 'khor lo dang g.yon
NK041(di)019:182: spyan ma dkar mo g.yas 'khor lo dang g.yon des
NK041(di)019:183: yu ba byas pa'i dril bu 'dzin pa dang mnyam
NK041(di)019:184: par sbyor ba / de bzhin du /
NK041(di)019:185: glegs bam rnams rma byas btegs pa'i rin po che'i
NK041(di)019:186: khri sna tshogs pad+ma dang nyi zla brtsegs pa'i steng
NK041(di)019:187: du am las pad+ma am gis mtshan pa las snang
NK041(di)019:188: ba mtha' yas dmar po g.yas pad+ma dang g.yon dril
NK041(di)019:189: bu 'dzin pa / gos dkar mo dmar mo g.yas
NK041(di)019:190: pad+ma dang g.yon des yu ba byas pa'i dril bu
NK041(di)019:191: 'dzin pa dang mnyam par sbyor ba /
NK041(di)019:192: phyag mtshan rnams glang pos btegs pa'i rin po che'i
NK041(di)019:193: khri sna tshogs pad+ma nyi zla brtsegs pa'i steng du
NK041(di)019:194: h'u las rdo rje h'u gis mtshan pa las mi
NK041(di)019:195: bskyod pa sngon po g.yas rdo rje dang g.yon dril
NK041(di)019:196: bu 'dzin pa / dbyings phyug ma sngon mo g.yas
NK041(di)019:197: rdo rje dang g.yon des yu ba byas pa'i dril
NK041(di)019:198: bu 'dzin pa dang mnyam par sbyor /
NK041(di)019:199: gzhan yang rin po che'i bye brag dang bang mdzod sogs rin 'byung /
NK041(di)019:200: go cha rol mo srung ba'i rigs sogs don grub tu bskyed par bshad do //
NK041(di)019:202: thams cad kyang zhi zhing 'dzum la mtshan dpe'i lang
NK041(di)019:203: tsho rab tu rgyas pa dar gyi na bza' dang
NK041(di)019:204: rin po che'i rgyan thams cad kyis brgyan cing 'od
NK041(di)019:205: zer mtha' yas par spro ba'i bdag nyid can du
NK041(di)019:206: bzhugs pa'o // de rnams kyi spyi bor dkar po /
NK041(di)019:208: thugs kar h'u sngon po rnams kyis mtshan par /
NK041(di)019:210: bdag dang rten gyi thugs ka'i h'u las 'od zer
NK041(di)019:211: 'phros pas ye shes kyi 'khor lo bsam gyis mi
NK041(di)019:212: khyab pa'i tshogs thams cad badz+ra sa ma dzah bzhi
NK041(di)019:214: ma lus sems can kun gyi mgon gyur cing //
NK041(di)019:215: bdud sde dpung bcas mi bzad 'joms mdzad lha //
NK041(di)019:216: dngos rnams ma lus ji bzhin mkhyen gyur pa'i //
NK041(di)019:217: bcom ldan 'khor bcas gnas 'dir gshegs su gsol //
NK041(di)019:218: ji ltar sangs rgyas rnams ni dga' ldan nas //
NK041(di)019:219: sprul pa dam pa tog dkar lha yi bus //
NK041(di)019:220: mi pham mgon la rgyal tshab dbang bskur nas //
NK041(di)019:221: gzigs pa rnam lngas 'dzam gling kun gzigs shing //
NK041(di)019:222: glang chen thal kar stabs gshegs lhums zhugs ltar //
NK041(di)019:223: rdo rje rin chen pad+ma'i rigs mchog dang //
NK041(di)019:224: las kyi rigs dang de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs //
NK041(di)019:225: phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba sras dang bcas pa rnams //
NK041(di)019:226: dus 'dir bdag gis dad pas spyan 'dren na //
NK041(di)019:227: rten mchog 'dir la 'byon par mdzad du gsol //
NK041(di)019:229: bdag dang 'gro la thugs brtse'i phyir //
NK041(di)019:230: nyid kyi rdzu 'phrul mthu yis ni //
NK041(di)019:231: ji srid mchod pa bdag bgyid na //
NK041(di)019:232: de srid bcom ldan bzhugs su gsol //
NK041(di)019:233: pad+ma ka ma l+aa ya s+t+wam gyis gdan 'bul /
NK041(di)019:235: shab+da pra t+aits+tsha s+w+aa h+aa 'i bar gyis mchod /
NK041(di)019:236: lnga pa dgug gzhug bya ba ni /
NK041(di)019:237: badz+ra am ku sha dzah badz+ra pa sha h'u /
NK041(di)019:239: badz+ra +aa be sha ya ho zhes pas dgug bcing mnyes dgyes pa bskyed /
NK041(di)019:241: dpal ldan sangs rgyas sku 'chang ba //
NK041(di)019:242: rdo rje mi phyed gsum gyi sku //
NK041(di)019:243: deng 'dir sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK041(di)019:244: sku yi dbyig tu dbang bskur ro //
NK041(di)019:245: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa k+aa ya badz+ra
NK041(di)019:246: s+w+aa b+h+aa wa at+ma ko&a hamh +aah dpal ldan sangs
NK041(di)019:248: rdo rje mi phyed gsum gyi gsung //
NK041(di)019:249: deng 'dir sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK041(di)019:250: gsung gi dbyig tu dbang bskur ro //
NK041(di)019:251: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa w+aak+ka badz+ra s+w+aa
NK041(di)019:252: b+h+aa wa at+ma ko&a hamh h'u dpal ldan sangs rgyas
NK041(di)019:253: thugs 'chang ba // rdo rje mi phyed gsum gyi thugs //
NK041(di)019:254: deng 'dir sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK041(di)019:255: thugs kyi dbyig tu dbang bskur ro //
NK041(di)019:256: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa tsit+ta badz+ra s+w+aa b+h+aa ad+ma ko&a ham /
NK041(di)019:258: bdun pa dang bskur ba ni /
NK041(di)019:259: rang gi snying ga'i sa bon las byung ba'i 'od
NK041(di)019:260: zer gyis dbang gi lha de bzhin gshegs pa rigs
NK041(di)019:261: lnga sras dang bcas pa thams cad badz+ra sa m+aa
NK041(di)019:262: dzah sa spyan drangs nas mdun gyi nam mkhar bzhugs
NK041(di)019:263: pa la / badz+ra ar+g+ham sogs nas /
NK041(di)019:266: chos sku nam mkha' bzhin du dbyer med kyang //
NK041(di)019:267: gzugs sku 'ja' tshon bzhin du so sor gsal //
NK041(di)019:268: thabs dang shes rab mchog la mnga' brnyes pa'i //
NK041(di)019:269: rigs lnga bde bar gshegs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK041(di)019:271: rdo rje can gyi sangs rgyas la //
NK041(di)019:272: 'gro ba skyob pa'i ched du dbang //
NK041(di)019:273: yon tan 'byung gnas ji ltar stsal //
NK041(di)019:274: de ltar 'di la'ang stsal du gsol //
NK041(di)019:275: zhes gsol ba btab pas nam mkha' gang ba'i de
NK041(di)019:276: bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyis dbang bskur ba'i dgongs pa
NK041(di)019:277: mdzod // yum rnams kyis bum pa'i chu rgyun gyis dbang bskur /
NK041(di)019:278: byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyis bkra shis pa'i glu dbyangs brjod /
NK041(di)019:279: lha mo rnams kyis gdugs dang ba dan la sogs pa bsgrengs shing /
NK041(di)019:280: rol mo'i sgra dang bcas pas mchod rdzas kyi char
NK041(di)019:281: 'bebs khro bo rnams kyis bgegs bskrad pa'i las mdzad
NK041(di)019:282: par bsam / bkra shis gang zhig sems can kun gyi snying la gnas //
NK041(di)019:283: kun gyi bdag nyid rigs byed kun gyi bdag po mchog /
NK041(di)019:284: ma lus sems can skyed mdzad bde ba chen po ste //
NK041(di)019:285: des ni deng khyod dbang bskur mchog la bkra shis shog /
NK041(di)019:287: ji ltar bltams pa tsam gyis ni /
NK041(di)019:289: de bzhin bdag gis dbang bskur ro //
NK041(di)019:290: sarba ta th+aa ga ta a b+hi she ka te sa ma ya sh+ri ye h'u /
NK041(di)019:291: zhes dbang bskur bas sku gang dri ma dag chu'i
NK041(di)019:292: lhag ma spyi bor 'khyil ba las rnam snang sogs
NK041(di)019:293: bdag por gyur pa'i rigs lngas dbu brgyan par bsam
NK041(di)019:294: / h'u t+r+aam hrih+aah pany+tsa ku la mu ku ta a b+hi shiny+tsa m+aam /
NK041(di)019:295: zhes dbu brgyan gyis dbang bskur /
NK041(di)019:297: badz+ra tush+ya ho zhes rdo rje thal mo mnyes par bya'o //
NK041(di)019:299: dngos su 'byor dang yid kyis rnam sprul pa'i //
NK041(di)019:300: kun tu bzang po bla med mchod sprin gyis //
NK041(di)019:301: mkha' dbyings rnam dag rgya cher yongs bkod de //
NK041(di)019:302: phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod pa rgya mtshos mchod //
NK041(di)019:303: sarba ta th+aa ga ta badz+ra ar+g+ham sogs nas shab+da pra t+aits+tsha s+w+aa h+aa'i bar gyis mchod /
NK041(di)019:304: chos sku nam mkha' sogs kyis bstod /
NK041(di)019:305: brgyad pa spyan dbye ba ni /
NK041(di)019:306: gser thur gyis dbye ba'i tshul dang bcas /
NK041(di)019:307: ji ltar mig mkhan rgyal po yis //
NK041(di)019:308: 'jig rten rab rib bsal ba ltar //
NK041(di)019:309: rgyal ba rnams kyi ye shes spyan //
NK041(di)019:310: sems can don du dbye bar bya //
NK041(di)019:311: tsakyu tsakyu sa man+ta tsakyu bi sho d+ha ni s+w+aa h+aa /
NK041(di)019:312: ye shes kyi spyan rnam par dag pa dang ldan
NK041(di)019:313: cing sems can gyi don la gzigs pa 'jug pa'i
NK041(di)019:314: mthu phun sum tshogs pa la mnga' brnyes par gyur
NK041(di)019:315: cig / dgu pa rten bsgyur ba ni /
NK041(di)019:316: slob dpon gyis rdo rje dang bcas pa'i thal mos
NK041(di)019:317: rten gyi gzugs brnyan me long gi dngos su shar
NK041(di)019:318: ba la reg cing se gol gyi sgras mtshon pas
NK041(di)019:321: bskyed pa'i lha yongs su gyur pa las sku gsung
NK041(di)019:322: thugs so so'i snang bsnyan gsal la ma 'dres pa
NK041(di)019:323: yongs su rdzogs pa'i mthu byin dang ldan par bsam
NK041(di)019:324: / bcu pa mnga' 'bul ba la bzhi las /
NK041(di)019:325: dang po mchod bstod kyis spyir mnga' dbul ba ni /
NK041(di)019:326: mchod pa bsang sbyangs byin rlabs sngon du 'gro bas /
NK041(di)019:330: lha mo bcu drug rnams spyi ltar 'bul /
NK041(di)019:332: phyogs bcu rab 'byams nam mkha'i khams gang ba'i //
NK041(di)019:333: mchod yon zhabs bsil me tog bdug spos dang //
NK041(di)019:334: mar me dri chab zhal zas rol mo sogs //
NK041(di)019:335: kun bzang rnam sprul mchod sprin rgya mtshos mchod //
NK041(di)019:336: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ar+g+ham pra tits+tsha pu dza
NK041(di)019:337: me g+ha sa mu dra s+pha ra na sa ma
NK041(di)019:339: shab+da'i bar sbyar bas nyer spyod /
NK041(di)019:340: mi dbang rin chen sna bdun 'di dag ni //
NK041(di)019:341: sangs rgyas sras dang bcas pa ma lus la //
NK041(di)019:342: bshams shing yid kyis sprul te phul ba yis //
NK041(di)019:343: 'gro ba mi zad gter la spyod par shog /
NK041(di)019:344: sab+ta ma h+aa rat+na badz+ra p+au dzi te +aahmh'u gis rin chen bdun /
NK041(di)019:345: phyogs dus kun na gzugs sgra dri dang ro //
NK041(di)019:346: reg bya'i khyad par phun sum tshogs pa rnams //
NK041(di)019:347: mos blos rgyal ba sras bcas la 'bul na //
NK041(di)019:348: bzhes shing bla med sgrub mchog stsal du gsol //
NK041(di)019:349: pany+tsa ka ma gu na badz+ra p+au dzi te +aahmh'u /
NK041(di)019:350: gis 'dod yon lnga rnams kyis mchod /
NK041(di)019:352: mnyam nyid mi g.yo sogs sangs rgyas spyi'i bstod pa'am /
NK041(di)019:354: chos sku nam mkha' sogs dang /
NK041(di)019:355: bstod par 'os pa thams cad la //
NK041(di)019:357: gnyis pa bye brag tu nye bar mkho na bas mnga' dbul ba ni /
NK041(di)019:358: man+dala gyi bkod pa dbul zhing /
NK041(di)019:359: sa gzhi spos chus byugs shing me tog bkram //
NK041(di)019:360: ri rab gling bzhi nyi zlas brgyan pa 'di //
NK041(di)019:361: sangs rgyas zhing du dmigs te phul ba yis //
NK041(di)019:362: 'gro kun rnam dag zhing la spyod par shog /
NK041(di)019:363: sarba ta th+aa ga ta rat+na man+da la +aahmh'u /
NK041(di)019:365: stong gsum kun tu dri ngad ldang ba yi //
NK041(di)019:366: dri mchog rnams kyis thub dbang rnams kyi sku //
NK041(di)019:367: gser sbyangs btso ma byi dor byas pa ltar //
NK041(di)019:368: 'od chags 'bar ba de dag byug par bgyi //
NK041(di)019:371: sna tshogs dbang po'i gzhu ltar rab bkra zhing //
NK041(di)019:372: gang la reg na bde ba'i rgyur 'gyur ba'i //
NK041(di)019:373: gos bzang rin chen bdag blo sbyangs phyir 'bul //
NK041(di)019:374: bzod pa dam pa'i gos kyis brgyan par shog /
NK041(di)019:377: rgya ba mtshan dpe'i rang bzhin rgyan ldan phyir //
NK041(di)019:378: rgyan gzhan dag gis brgyan par mi 'tshal yang //
NK041(di)019:379: rin chen rgyan mchog phul bas 'gro kun gyis //
NK041(di)019:380: mtshan dpes brgyan pa'i sku mchog thob par shog /
NK041(di)019:381: badz+ra bi shwa rat+na +aa lam ka ra ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK041(di)019:382: gsum pa tsa ru'i zhal zas kyis mnga' dbul ba ni /
NK041(di)019:383: lha bshos gtsang ma ting chab kyis bran la /
NK041(di)019:384: na mas+sarba ta th+aa ga ta sogs nam mkha' mdzod sngags rgya lan gsum gyis byin gyis brlabs la /
NK041(di)019:385: rin po che las grub pa'i snod yangs shing rgya
NK041(di)019:386: che ba'i nang du lha rdzas kyi zhal zas 'dod
NK041(di)019:387: yon gyi dngos po zad mi shes pa bdud rtsi'i
NK041(di)019:388: rgya mtsho chen por gyur bar bsams la /
NK041(di)019:389: zhal zas ro brgya ldan zhing yid 'phrog pa //
NK041(di)019:390: legs sbyar 'di ni rgyal ba sras bcas la //
NK041(di)019:391: dad pas phul bas 'gro ba 'di dag kun //
NK041(di)019:392: 'byor ldan ting 'dzin zas la spyod par shog /
NK041(di)019:394: bzhi pa sngags kyis mnga' dbul ba ni /
NK041(di)019:395: rten rnams la gzungs thag ser po btags pa'i sne mo nas slob dpon gyis bzung zhing /
NK041(di)019:396: gnas bya'i rten rnams kyi thugs kar zla ba la
NK041(di)019:397: gnas pa'i sngags phreng 'khor ba'i 'od zer gyis phyogs
NK041(di)019:398: bcu'i rgyal ba sras dang bcas pa rten sa so
NK041(di)019:399: so'i rnam par byon nas de la bzhugs par gyur
NK041(di)019:401: bdag bskyed kyi snying po'i mthar /
NK041(di)019:402: su pra tish+tha dang h'u h+r+aihb+h+r+aum kham badz+r+ai b+ha wa dri d+ha tish+tha b+h+r+aum kham s+w+aa h+aa /
NK041(di)019:404: rten 'brel snying po rnams ci nus bzla /
NK041(di)019:407: phun sum tshogs pa mnga' ba sogs pa'i shis pa
NK041(di)019:408: rgya cher brjod pas mnga' gsol zhing me tog gi
NK041(di)019:409: char phab / bcu gcig pa gsol ba gdab pa ni /
NK041(di)019:410: yi ge brgya pa lan gsum sngon du 'gro bas /
NK041(di)019:411: me tog dam pa phreng ba dam pa dang /
NK041(di)019:412: sogs shwa lo ka gnyis kyis mchod /
NK041(di)019:413: de dag basngagasa pa sogs kyis bstod /
NK041(di)019:414: rten la me tog gi phreng ba btags pa nas bzung /
NK041(di)019:415: thal mo sbyar bas btud de /
NK041(di)019:416: ji srid sa chu me dang ni //
NK041(di)019:417: rlung gi bskal pas 'jig bar du //
NK041(di)019:418: sems can kun gyi don gyi phyir //
NK041(di)019:419: bcom ldan khyod ni bzhugs par mdzod //
NK041(di)019:420: 'dir ni gzugs dang lhan cig tu //
NK041(di)019:421: 'gro ba'i don du bzhugs nas kyang //
NK041(di)019:422: nad med tshe dang dbang phyug dang //
NK041(di)019:423: mchog rnams legs par stsal du gsol //
NK041(di)019:425: phyogs bcu na bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad bdag la dgongs su gsol //
NK041(di)019:426: ji srid nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam pa'i sems can
NK041(di)019:427: thams cad mi gnas pa'i mya ngan las 'das pa'i
NK041(di)019:428: sa la ma bzhag gi bar du rgyal ba rnams
NK041(di)019:429: mya ngan las mi 'da' bar brtan par bzhugs su
NK041(di)019:430: gsol / khyad par du'ang sku gsung thugs kyi rten
NK041(di)019:431: 'di rnams la ji srid 'byung ba bzhi'i gnod pas
NK041(di)019:432: ma zhig gi bar du brtan par bzhugs su gsol
NK041(di)019:433: gsol / / brtan par bzhugs nas kyang bdag dang
NK041(di)019:434: sems can thams cad la mchog thun mong gi dngos
NK041(di)019:435: grub ma lus pa stsal du gsol /
NK041(di)019:436: lan gsum gyis gsol ba gdab /
NK041(di)019:437: rten 'brel snying po bzlas pa'i me tog 'thor ba /
NK041(di)019:438: slar yang mchod bstod kyang bya'o //
NK041(di)019:439: gsum pa rjes kyi cho ga la drug las /
NK041(di)019:440: dang po gtor ma btang ba ni /
NK041(di)019:441: nang du rdo rje'i chos srung rnams dang /
NK041(di)019:442: phyi rol tu phyogs skyong 'byung po rnams la gtor ma cho ga ji ltar rigs pas 'bul lo //
NK041(di)019:443: gnyis pa srung ma bsgo ba ni /
NK041(di)019:444: gnas dang rten gang la gnyer gtad par 'dod pa
NK041(di)019:445: de nyid kyi gtor ma zur du bshams nas phul
NK041(di)019:446: / rdo rje bka' nan gyi rgya bcings te /
NK041(di)019:448: rdo rje rtse lnga pa'i rgya spyi bor reg pa'i mos pas /
NK041(di)019:449: badz+ra sa ma ya ha na ha na h'u phata ces pas dam la gzhag /
NK041(di)019:450: rdo rje'i chos skyong ba'i srung ma 'khor dang bcas pa khyed rnams kyis /
NK041(di)019:451: gnas dang rten 'di rnams srung zhing skyong ba dang /
NK041(di)019:452: mchod pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa rgyun mi 'chad par 'byung ba'i phrin las mdzod cig /
NK041(di)019:454: gsum pa dkyil 'khor gyi rjes kyi bya ba ni las gzhung ltar bya'o //
NK041(di)019:455: bzhi pa yon bdag bsgo ba ni /
NK041(di)019:456: bkra shis pa'i rdzas dang mchod pa'i yo byad 'du
NK041(di)019:457: byas nas yon bdag nye logs su ston bzang po
NK041(di)019:458: la 'khod par / bder gshegs lhag ma 'di dag ni //
NK041(di)019:459: gsol zhig sdig pa byang bar 'gyur //
NK041(di)019:460: zhes brjod cing dpon slob thams cad la tsa ru'i bza' ba 'grim /
NK041(di)019:461: slob dpon gyis spro na spyi dang bye brag gi
NK041(di)019:462: lung gis rgyab skyor te skabs su babs pa'i bshad
NK041(di)019:465: khyod kyis nga la gang gsol ba'i //
NK041(di)019:466: sku gzugs dag ni khyad par du //
NK041(di)019:467: ji ltar gsungs pa ji bzhin du //
NK041(di)019:468: de dag don ni ngas byas te //
NK041(di)019:469: de rnams don ni grub zin gyi //
NK041(di)019:470: ci bder bar ni mchod par byos //
NK041(di)019:471: khyod kyis nga la gang gsol ba btab pa'i rab
NK041(di)019:472: tu gnas pa de legs par tshang bar byas kyi
NK041(di)019:473: / khyod kyis rten 'di rnams la zhag bdun du mchod pa rgya chen po gyis shig /
NK041(di)019:474: de nas kyang ci 'byor pa'i mchod pa rgyun mi chad par gyis shig /
NK041(di)019:476: des kyang mchod pa'i bye brag rnams la gang gis
NK041(di)019:477: bstar te rten gyi drung du bkod pas mdzes par
NK041(di)019:478: bshams la / dpon slob rnams mgrin gcig par bsang sbyang byin rlabs sngon du 'gro bas /
NK041(di)019:479: rab 'byams rgya mtsho sogs tshigs bcad sngags dang bcas pa ji ltar rigs pas 'bul /
NK041(di)019:480: lnga pa shis par bya ba ni /
NK041(di)019:481: bgegs bsal ba'i slad du sbyang ba gsum sngar bzhin la /
NK041(di)019:483: bden pa chen po'i byin gyis brlabs kyis zhes pa'i mtshams /
NK041(di)019:484: deng 'dir rab gnas par byas pa'i rten rnams dang /
NK041(di)019:485: sbyin pa'i bdag po 'khor dang bcas pa la bkra shis pa dang /
NK041(di)019:486: mthun rkyen bsod nams kyi legs tshogs spel ba la
NK041(di)019:487: bar du gcod cing glags lta ba'i sogs sngon du
NK041(di)019:488: 'gro bas / rdzas dang sbyin bdag rnams /
NK041(di)019:491: stong pa'i ngang las sbyin pa'i bdag po skad cig
NK041(di)019:492: gis gnod sbyin bye ba'i sde dpon chen po dzam
NK041(di)019:493: b+ha la'i skur gyur pa'i mdun du mam las byung
NK041(di)019:494: ba'i bkra shis pa'i rdzas brgyad so so'i las sgrub
NK041(di)019:495: pa la thogs pa med pa'i nus pa dang ldan
NK041(di)019:496: par gyur / +aahmang+ga lam dra bya h'u /
NK041(di)019:498: me long ye shes rgya mtsho chen po ste //
NK041(di)019:499: zhes sogs kyis rdzas rnams re re bzhin du yon bdag la gtad cing /
NK041(di)019:500: des kyang rten la 'bul ba'i tshul bya /
NK041(di)019:501: slar yang mdun gyi nam mkhar phyogs dus kyi rgyal ba sras dang bcas pa rnams dang /
NK041(di)019:502: lha dang drang srong bden tshig grub pa'i tshogs kyis
NK041(di)019:503: shis pa brjod pa'i glu dbyangs di ri ri sgrogs
NK041(di)019:504: shing me tog man+d+h+aa ra'i char chen po phab pas
NK041(di)019:505: dge legs kyi snang bas sa gsum kun tu khyab
NK041(di)019:506: par byas pa'i mos pa mdzod /
NK041(di)019:507: phun sum tshogs pa mnga' ba sogs kyis shis brjod dang dga' ston rgya cher bya /
NK041(di)019:508: drug pa dge ba bsngo ba ni /
NK041(di)019:509: de ltar bsgrubs pa'i dge legs byas kyis mtshon te
NK041(di)019:510: dus gsum du bsags pa'i dge ba'i rtsa ba rnams
NK041(di)019:511: bla na med pa'i byang chub kyi ched du bzang
NK041(di)019:512: po bzhi ldan gyi yongs su bsngo bas rgyas gdabs
NK041(di)019:513: pa dang / smon lam gyi mthun 'gyur kyang ji ltar rigs pa rgyas par bya'o //
NK041(di)019:514: gal te de las bsdus par 'dod na /
NK041(di)019:515: bdag bskyed sngon du 'gro bas las bum sgrub /
NK041(di)019:516: sbyang ba nas brtsams te rten bsgyur ba'i bar sngar bzhin la /
NK041(di)019:517: mchod bstod dang sngags kyis mnga' dbul /
NK041(di)019:518: gsol gdab bcas kyi mthar bdag bskyed kyi rjes chog rnams bya'o //
NK041(di)019:520: bdag nyid skad cig gis rdo rje h'u mdzad du gsal zhing bden stobs brjod pas bgegs sbyang /
NK041(di)019:521: grub na rten rnying pa la lha khrus gsol ba'i chus khrus kyi bya ba mdor bsdus bya /
NK041(di)019:522: rten bskyed nas dbang bskur yan sngar ltar la /
NK041(di)019:526: gsol gdab bcas kyi mthar bkra shis pa'i me tog char du bsnyil bas grub pa yin no //
NK041(di)019:527: dam tshig gi gzugs brnyan sprul pa'i dkyil 'khor du /
NK041(di)019:528: ye shes lhag par gnas pa'i cho ga ni /
NK041(di)019:529: snying por dril te legs par sbyar ba'i dgos //
NK041(di)019:530: 'gro kun phan bde'i dga' ston rgyas gyur cig /
NK041(di)019:531: ces pa'ang mkhas shing grub pa brnyes pa'i rdo rje'i
NK041(di)019:532: slob dpon rnams kyis ji ltar bkral ba'i gzhung rgya
NK041(di)019:533: chen po las / gnas skabs 'ga' zhig tu mdor
NK041(di)019:534: bsdus pa'i tshul gyis cho ga'i yan lag ma nyams
NK041(di)019:535: par sgrub par 'dod pa rnams la smon pa'i bsam
NK041(di)019:537: sh+aakya'i dge slong rig pa 'dzin pa many+dzu g+ho shas
NK041(di)019:538: legs par sbyar ba'i dge bas 'jig rten gsum na
NK041(di)019:539: dge legs kyis snang bas dus rtag tu khyab pa'i
